Class Supervisor

java.lang.Object
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.supervisor.Supervisor
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class Supervisor extends Object implements ISupervisor
The Class Supervisor defines logic to coordinate a group of agents.

Heinz Stadler, Melinda Betz (minor contribution), Phil Heger (minor contribution)
